{"tid":1327838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「721文宣」  再次呼籲警員 及指引","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T09:54:41.000Z","uid":268619,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b7501853d330515e7e6c791a07d998609d9e2ece","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"由612起  見到衝突越演越激烈<br />\n經過一連串不合理事件<br />\n好多巴打絲打都覺得  無一個警察係無辜<br />\n什至已經打算係721豁出去<br />\n<br />\n警員需要立即醒覺 負責個個應該係林<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政治問題需要政治解決</span></strong><br />\n唔好再受到政府擺佈 成為政權嘅犧牲品<br />\n相信好多心存善意參與遊行 巴打絲打都唔希望搞出人命傷亡<br />\n<br />\n為左減少不必要傷亡 我覺得大家有必要再次呼籲尚存理性既警員<br />\n1. 可以選擇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工/請假</span></strong><br />\n2. 當值時 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應佩帶委任證</span></strong> 顯示自已合法地執行職務 <br />\n(如果你無展示警員身份 同時追打示威人仕 將有可能成為目標)<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要使用武力</span></strong> 收起警棍/武器 以免進一步刺激示威人仕 <br />\n4. 如不想參與無謂打鬥 應<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>與示威者保持安全距離</strong> </span><br />\n5. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">酌情 給予示威人仕 安全離開</span></strong>  逼人太甚 危險就會加大<br />\n6. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不進入私人地方</span></strong>(包括民居/商場/食肆) 因為最後理虧只會係你自已<br />\n7. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">讓記者進行採訪</span></strong> <br />\n(你越擋 只會令記者有更多寫作空間 咁多鏡頭你根本擋唔住真相)<br />\n<br />\n如果你行得正 企得正 又有委任證 又禮待香港市民 根本唔需要擔心人身安全<br />\n之前一連串不合理事件  就算你俾人鬧都係應該 請保持自身專業 盡量心平氣和 <br />\n你收到既怒氣  唔應該發洩去市民到 你可以向林鄭發洩 向高層發洩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你都係打分工 無謂揾條命去搏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waVxgFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaVxgFn.png&h=b8913dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[7.21 遊行] 好撚重要 必需置頂!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327475/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327475/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f54cdc727551fd847dd3a375ec9a77c93ae5aba6","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab121d2155b8db6f16f3419a175c6a6b7aeb4593","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:55:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c899cf55350ee7b1725ccc79738027778813807","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6cc06d8ae34f21b7059b9e837f837c06b1660725","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"035430a023be64d4b8101173b874e601fc89ce42","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:00:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5029adcd8fe0cbedf858a6fef01a148e19729599","tid":1327838,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a829ce13547a5dbe7cce98bc86eb4ee9bd0c887","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3e35459d5d76444c147e036e8906370bdc84dfcd","tid":1327838,"uid":211807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8118dff46b5bbc777b2725a811d1d52b7595ece2","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:05:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"6ded3fd3acb12d3a6cb6eddf88568fbb56162a94","tid":1327838,"uid":271088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"094bcf904e35696f740bb3b511cd1946ad7e3daf","tid":1327838,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:08:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"daf8a392ca5c7c87652b044c2aa5c8b72c607a8b","tid":1327838,"uid":268619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"暴力根本唔可以解決